Factorio.ElectricNetworkManager::prepare+6: 86 41 60        - xchg [rcx+60],al
Factorio.ElectricNetworkManager::prepare+9: C3              - ret 
Factorio.ElectricNetworkManager::prepare+A: CC              - int 3 
