Factorio.exe+2ECB4C: CC              - int 3 
Factorio.exe+2ECB4D: CC              - int 3 
Factorio.exe+2ECB4E: CC              - int 3 
Factorio.exe+2ECB4F: CC              - int 3 
// ---------- INJECTING HERE ----------
Factorio.ElectricNetworkManager::update: 48 89 5C 24 08  - mov [rsp+08],rbx
// ---------- DONE INJECTING  ----------
