Factorio.RecipeSlot::RecipeSlot+1A2
cmp byte ptr [r8+0A],0
Factorio.CraftingGui::updateCounts+273
cmp byte ptr [rsi+0A],0
Cursor Offset for Character: 0x490
Item:
+0x0 dword Item Count
+0x4 word Item ID
